{"tid":2021897,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓光州事件40周年 文在寅表示將全力查明真相","createTime":"2020-05-18T04:24:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T04:35:09.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"15eca72d5c21fc90688328ae6940e7b8f2972a12","tid":2021897,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T04:24:49.000Z","msg":"南韓光州事件40周年 文在寅表示將全力查明真相<br />\n18.05.2020 11:22<br />\n<br />\n南韓「光州事件」40周年，總統文在寅於光州市的「518」民主廣場，出席紀念儀式並致辭，表示政府將全力以赴查明事件真相，強調要調查誰人下令向民眾開火，以及戒嚴軍屠殺無辜平民，並動用直升機對民眾開槍的情況等。文在寅呼籲加害者協助調查，說如果加害者鼓起勇氣坦白，必能獲得寬恕，並走上和解之路，表示查明真相不在於處罰，而是要正確記錄歷史。<br />\n<br />\n韓聯社報道，1980年「光州事件」又稱「518民主化運動」，當時光州民眾要求推翻軍事獨裁政府，還政於民，掌握軍權的全斗煥政府血腥鎮壓，造成大量平民傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288254&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1288254%26csid%3D261_367&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCVR4K0ufT%2FFGu3kbIPb6xA8%3D&h=900362a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288254&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"d4ea6c5a316463a14616f7d5c7b23204c1909bcf","tid":2021897,"uid":143621,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T04:26:07.000Z","msg":"cls 直升機射平民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa095e02b325c3b61bef3c3320a94fefbee8a5c9","tid":2021897,"uid":301100,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T04:35:09.000Z","msg":"處決左全斗煥先講野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}